      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend road trips. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for a new owner to take the wheel. Come by, take it for a spin, and see why I\u2019ve enjoyed it so much!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
