    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies. This unit is mated to a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a variable M differential lock. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS system has been professionally serviced to maintain optimal camshaft timing. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings, and the engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with the signature metallic rasp. A mechanically sorted, driver-spec icon for the purist who values visceral feedback and analog performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
