    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-cared-for model that balances performance with everyday reliability. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, though close inspection will show some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the interior is clean and well-preserved; the upholstery shows light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster but remains free of rips or odors. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and the premium audio system, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a documented history of regular oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The brakes are responsive, and the tires still offer plenty of grip for the seasons ahead. It drives straight and true, offering a comfortable yet connected feel. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 29850.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
